title: [Higher Thinking, Loft]
description: Through wide gaps in the wooden planks of the floor, you notice patrons milling about and overhear their soft chatter as they examine their wares.  The walls of the room, comprised entirely of driftwood, are awkwardly shaped, the constant sea breeze occasionally wafting through the gaps in their structure.  A fine layer of sawdust, evidence of the building's recent construction, convers every surface in this space.
